gomodel:SYNGO_1232  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: Figure 5: Syn 2 is enriched in the synaptic vesicle fraction\n\n24/10/2017 Pim\n- Authors note; \"Proteins with an iTRAQ ratio of more than 2.5 are considered to be significantly enriched in the docked synaptic vesicle fraction.\"\n- Based on the known lipid binding domain of the protein, the \"extrinsic component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: Result section, First sentence: To isolate docking complexes from RAT brain, we first prepared synaptosomes and subjected them to limited proteolysis to dissociate pre- and postsynaptic membranes" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-9900-4233" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
